                <p>Patron's Golf Course Extension Road office provides 12A/80G compliance, FCRA accounting, CSR tracking, and trust audit. For registration, see <a href="/ngo-registration">NGO Registration</a>. For general accounting, see <a href="/accounting-services/gurugram">Accounting Services Gurugram</a>.</p>
